                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210214-137-off831 t18210214-137-crimeloc834"></join>. On the 27th of January, about seven o'clock in the evening, I was in the counting-house, and this beef was stolen from the shop-board.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210214-137-person1376">
                  ABRAHAM 
                  POLLY
               <interp inst="t18210214-137-person1376" type="surname" value="POLLY"></interp>
