                     <interp inst="t18210214-137-person1376" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner with another lad, who took the beef, and put it in the prisoner's apron; I followed, and caught him with it. I had watched them for an hour and a half.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM BANTING. I am a patrol. I was going my<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182102140052"></xptr>rounds, and heard the call of watch, ran over, and found the prisoner in charge with the beef.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. They all swear false, I never had it.</p>
